<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-07-10T11:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-07-10T11:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T11:00:00-04:00</updated><title>第一支全四肢瘫痪的电子竞技队创造了公平的竞争环境</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;四神中的理查德·雅各布斯和塞尔吉奥·阿塞维多&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/byh1xfCXIbeSwr7jCL_1cvtotX0=/76x0:904x552/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73453079/richard_jacobs_left_sergio_acevedo_right_.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 HBO 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;导演 Jess Jacklin 与 The Verge 谈论她继第一部之后的新纪录片 -四肢瘫痪的电子竞技队。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195198/quad-gods-documentary-jess-jacklin-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195198/quad-gods-documentary-jess-jacklin-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195198/quad-gods-documentary-jess-jacklin-interview</id><author><name>奥德白</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:35:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:35:02-04:00</updated><title>诉讼称现代经销商被迫推销“假”电动汽车销售</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;现代经销店&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-d_KzeXYCLmcb__dQ2F1O6y8GiI=/107x0:1253x764/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/73453039/2020_11_05.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Napleton Aurora Imports&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;umRGQm&quot;>;现代向经销商施压，要求“人为夸大”其电动汽车销量数据一项新的诉讼称，建立了一种制度，对“配合”的经销商给予奖励，而那些拒绝配合的经销商则受到“惩罚”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XOxdU9&quot;>;该诉讼由伊利诺伊州的 Napleton Aurora Imports 及其附属特许经营商向芝加哥联邦法院提起，诉讼称现代汽车已发布大量新闻稿，兜售“虚假”数字，这些数字旨在显示电动汽车销量同比增长。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BYnhgV&quot;>;拒绝参与所谓诡计的经销商将处于竞争劣势，包括被迫推销不受欢迎的车辆或拒绝为客户提供批发价格折扣。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ydjsjv&quot;>;&lt;q>;“这是一个错误的叙述。”&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/ div>; &lt;p id=&quot;k0FmUQ&quot;>;现代“强调...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195650/hyundai-fake -ev-sales-dealer-lawsuit&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195650/hyundai-fake-ev-sales-dealer-lawsuit" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195650/hyundai-fake-ev-sales-dealer-lawsuit</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:32:22-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:32:22-04:00</updated><title>如何预订三星 Galaxy Watch 7、Galaxy Watch Ultra 和 Galaxy Ring</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bAEPgP8WYBUNoDG8U-iIPrHR77Q=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73453027/Watch_and_Ring_from_Vjeran_Pavic.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片由 Alex Parkin / The Verge 和三星拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;I2GEQ0&quot;>;三星不仅仅是宣布 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds#stream-entry-669d21f5- 39e5-4398-a7fb-3da8f124c566&quot;>;新款可折叠手机&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai- z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds#stream-entry-cb1241d9-efae-451b-b9e5-16ff3108b8f5&quot;>;无线耳机&lt;/a>;在周三的三星 Unpacked 活动中，还有一系列新产品可穿戴设备：Galaxy Watch 7（299.99 美元）、Samsung Ring（399.99 美元）和 Samsung Galaxy Watch Ultra（649.99 美元）。虽然您必须等到 7 月 24 日才能正式上市，但所有可穿戴设备现在都可以在美国预订。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;juFBrU&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星 Galaxy Unpacked：夏季产品活动的所有新闻&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung- Galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星 Galaxy Watch 6 系列评测：精致，但并非革命性&quot;,&quot;url&quot;: &quot;https://www.theverge.com/23818557/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-review-bezels-smartwatch-wearables&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= &quot;geO0A2&quot;>;新款可穿戴设备面向广泛的受众，从休闲用户到户外运动员。三星 Galaxy Ring 是一款时尚的可穿戴设备，更像是一款谨慎的健康追踪器，而 Galaxy Watch 7 是一款智能手表，功能更强大&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195618 /the-galaxy-watch-ultra-get-fda-cleared-sleep-apnea-detection&quot;>;新的睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能&lt;/a>;。但它的功能并不像三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 那样丰富，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung -galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:23:37-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:23:37-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy 拆封：2024 年 7 月活动中宣布的所有内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色、蓝色和水绿色背景上的三星徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/j30lXEiclgq_A3r3_h4CIMAulZo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452722/acastro_STK075_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;三星推出了 Galaxy Ring、Galaxy Watch Ultra、新款 Z Fold 和 Z Flip 手机等。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>宋茜</name><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>最高法院 NetChoice 裁决的后果</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;最高法院大楼的照片插图，带有像素化的红白条纹。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-_j8bu4miMeay7jIXHchVU4QLYw=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452898/STK463_SCOTUS_D.0.jpg&quot;/ >; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |照片来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;以下是 SCOTUS 的决定对从儿童在线安全法到 TikTok“禁令”等各个方面可能意味着的含义。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195235/scotus-netchoice-kosa-kids-safety-age-verification-tiktok-ban</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>索尼新款 ZV-E10 II 相机旨在让视频博主远离 1,000 美元的手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色的索尼 ZV-E10 II，坐在桌子上，镜头已拆卸。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RzXhtCLNqP3vNHyi2owvJdAN2vk=/0x0:7726x5151/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452911/BFARSACE_ZVE10II_1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;ZV-E10 II 看起来非常像其 2021 年的前身。&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7Gv7iG&quot;>;涓滴经济可能很垃圾，但索尼对于相机中的技术，仍然是坚定的信徒。新款 ZV-E10 II 延续了索尼的趋势，即从昂贵的相机到更实惠的型号进行小规模的迭代改变。只是它永远不会没有一些权衡。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;4LKvq5&quot;>;ZV-E10 II 是 APS-C 无反光镜系统相机的后续产品 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22702421/sony-alpha-zv-e10-review-vlogging-camera-test-price-specs&quot;>;2021 年的 ZV-E10&lt;/a>;，现在配备更大的电池、26 兆像素背照式传感器，并改进了 4K 视频。它还会&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1838825-REG%2Fsony_zv_e10_ii_mirrorless_camera。 html&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F10%2F24194506%2Fsony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot; rel= “赞助的 nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;主体费用为 999 美元&lt;/a>; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A% 2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1839377-REG%2Fsony_zv_e10_ii_mirrorless_camera.html&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F10%2F24194506% 2F索尼- alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;捆绑包售价 1,099 美元&lt;/a>; 搭配索尼新款 PZ 16-50mm f/3.5-5.6 OSS II 镜头于 8 月初推出 - 价格大约是旗舰手机的价格，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899983/iphone-15-pro-max-camera-apple-full-框架&quot;>;iPhone 15 Pro Max&lt;/a>;。但是，当然，即使是最好的 iPhone 相机也有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii -vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 有较小的更新和更高的价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 智能手机的上手照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I66riB7OyE8CUtS7R-uBM9xNMu4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452748/DSCF8089.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;炎热的可折叠夏天正如火如荼地进行，你们大家。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;opCbaW&quot;>;如果您还有任何剩余的希望，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/ 3/24191966/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-spec-leak&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188017/ samsung-galaxy-z-flip-fold-6-leak-renders-colors-unpacked&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>;，三星的可折叠手机今年将进行重大更新，那么我不想成为坏消息的传播者。它们更耐用一点，更轻一点，并且有一些微小的升级。即便如此，这两款机型&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cmDKOyRtZR8&quot;>;都获得了一定程度的提升&lt;/a>;：价格上涨，Galaxy Z Fold 6 现在起价为 1,899 美元，Z Flip 起价为6 件售价 1,099 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WjhfvK&quot;>;两款手机均采用专门为三星调校的 Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 芯片组，与 S24 系列一样，它们都包含七年的操作系统和安全更新支持。由于铰链设计和材料的改进，它们都更加坚固，并声称具有更好的抗跌落能力。内部柔性玻璃也更耐用，而且...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z- Fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 上手体验：超级似曾相识</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Galaxy Watch Ultra 视图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lVAlvegcCx6horuGR3JrU5QVcC4=/0x0:4032x2688/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/73452769/galaxywatchultra4.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;肯定是松鼠画。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这是 Apple Watch Ultra，但适用于 Android。哦，Galaxy Watch 7 也在这里。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-功能价格&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-features-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-features-price</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星新款 Galaxy Buds 在形式和功能上都是公然的 AirPod 克隆</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Buds 3 / Galaxy Buds 3 Pro 的实际产品照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/26UyHrvmjER1lhrtKzJzqbOWzsE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452746/DSCF8067_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UZHf7M&quot;>;除了最新的折叠手机和可穿戴设备外，三星还推出了新款 Galaxy Buds 3 Pro 和 Galaxy Buds 3。 com/2024/7/5/24192554/someone-already-bought-samsungs-galaxy-buds3-pro&quot;>;和早期销售&lt;/a>;）证实，该公司已经放弃了过去几代的微妙入耳式设计茎状外观赋予它们类似 AirPods 的外观和感觉——尤其是白色。两款耳塞均采用青铜灰色饰面，与棱角分明的“刀片”设计相结合，让我想起了特斯拉的 Cyber​​truck。但不可否认的是，它与苹果广受欢迎的 AirPods 总体上有相似之处。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;D8k3an&quot;>;三星的新闻稿称，这一转变是“收集到的各种统计数据”的直接结果，这些数据表明柄形因素可产生更好的舒适度和入耳稳定性。所以，我们在这里......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04